Author: GeoffreyIsWet
Text: Fr. I have a friend who has a habit of sending me those gross Bestgore type videos that get posted on Facebook for a short period of time before being taken down. She sent me one tonight and I was like "wish you'd stop sending me these when I just happen to be eating" Her: "well then stop eating lmao" My overly sensitive disordered ass reacting to her innocent sarcasm: :) OK :)  Some people don't realise the implications of their words but at the same time our disorders have a tendency to cause us to twist and misinterpret them anyway

Author: quietlyinteresting
Text: People say things sometimes so vague they don't really mean what they say.  Don't let one throw away comment define you or limit your dreams.   Don't let this stay with you too long since its autumn let this comment fall away like a leaf and be blown away.   Live your dreams.
